                            </FooterDetails>
                            <Heading/>
                            <Paragraph>The ATSDR, as part of the Public Health Service,
                                        reduces exposure to toxic substances—exposure to substances
                                        from wastesites, unplanned releases, and other pollution
                                        sources that are present in the environment—which produce
                                        adverse health effects and diminish the quality of
                                        life.</Paragraph>
